HEADWORD: frogmarch
<hw>frogmarch</hw> <pos>v.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>to march a person
against his will by any method.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>to carry someone against his will upside down such
that each limb is held by one person.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

